# HSM collector stress conformance.
# Keep this fixture bounded enough for every language port to run in a normal PR.
# Format: case|action|arg1|arg2|arg3|arg4

sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|create_collector
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|create_int_sensors|32|contract/stress/sequential
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|start
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|add_int_sequence|32|100|0|Ok|sequential-load
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|expect_sent_count|3200|10
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Comment":"sequential-load"

